{"tid":675433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"追人還錢好似殺人父母咁","createTime":"2018-05-23T13:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T14:05:25.000Z","uid":111860,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1250949ae0d47790cf90c4a2f9112311cbc696b0","tid":675433,"uid":111860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:25:35.000Z","msg":"成日追人還錢已經追到厭<br />\n明明追人還係理所當然，點解追人還錢好似乞食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次借幾十幾十咁，越借越多，都唔知差幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但成日見到借錢果啲朋友會有額外錢買啲非實用野（課金，耳機等等）<br />\n巴絲身邊有無咁既朋友/同事"},{"pid":"9ee6b25db78f6d082875d3c43b16853e28f966bd","tid":675433,"uid":118851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3e36336dbef1a95fd76ebd3e21b04a6bd7fced","tid":675433,"uid":90936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"我中學嗰陣都係借錢比人。幫佢比補習費，買波飛我幫佢比錢，平時同同學一齊岀街睇戲食飯又幫佢岀住錢先。夾夾埋埋4K <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n宜家讀大專，追咗咁多年都只係還咗500比我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n追數追到好似佢老母咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c783bf52b0b5b327e6ba5523fbf071997d30383a","tid":675433,"uid":137810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:32:45.000Z","msg":"成日借幾十幾十比人 特登追返又好似好小家 唔追自己積積埋埋又冇左一筆 所以依家都唔會借錢比人廢事傷感情"},{"pid":"a7577d8e0834a6fa108a4f79e6de00f3155b5f81","tid":675433,"uid":144466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:36:40.000Z","msg":"從來唔會借錢俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd446c2eb0a85852d648e002d28801e3f3f50ba","tid":675433,"uid":278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T14:05:25.000Z","msg":"所以最多借人500以下<br />\n話借多過嘅 絕交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}